<body><div><div class="affidavit-title">AFFIDAVIT</div>
<p style="font-family:'Book Antiqua',serif;font-size:12pt;text-align:justify;margin-bottom:6pt;"><b>Munimadugu Vighnesh Prasad</b>, <b>S/o ewqe</b>, aged <b>21 years</b> residing at 78-112 krishna nagar kurnool
beside sri devi mla house near dolphin bakery kurnool do hereby affirm and state as follows:</p>
<ol style="font-family:'Book Antiqua',serif;font-size:12pt;margin:4pt 0 4pt 24pt;">
  <li style="margin-bottom:4pt;">I, <b>Munimadugu Vighnesh Prasad</b> have floated a Partnership Firm with <b>Munimadugu Vighnesh Prasad</b> as the partner to carry on the business under the name and style of <b>"wqeqe"</b>.</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:4pt;">The said Firm commenced the business from 13th day of February 2132 and the office of the firm is situated at 78-112 krishna nagar kurnool and the said premises belong to me.</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:4pt;">The said firm has applied for Registration to the Registrar of Firms, 321.</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:4pt;">I have no objection and give my consent and acceptance for running the said firm in my building and I am not collecting any rent from the said firm because I am also one of the partners in the firm.</li>
</ol>
<p style="font-family:'Book Antiqua',serif;font-size:12pt;text-align:justify;margin:10pt 0 6pt;">Solemnly affirmed at 321 on this day 13-02-2123.</p>
<div style="margin-top:18pt;text-align:right;"><div style="border-bottom:1pt solid #000;display:inline-block;width:160pt;margin-top:8pt;"></div><br><b>DEPONENT</b></div>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:10pt;font-size:11pt;"><span>Place: 321</span><span>Date: 13-02-2123</span></div></div></body></html>